WEBVTT

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:55.000
Here.

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:56.280
Sister Man, try the water.

00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:57.679
It's fine.

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:04.439
Asi.

00:01:04.799 --> 00:01:05.879
While you're young,

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.000
you should go out and see the world.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.159
I don't know how to do anything.

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:10.359
What could I do out there?

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.040
Silly Kiddo.

00:01:12.519 --> 00:01:15.280
Youth and beauty are a woman's greatest assets.

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:17.319
You know? You can't waste them.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.680
How much do you make a year right now?

00:01:21.319 --> 00:01:22.079
Not much.

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:26.000
Guess.

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:28.680
How much this bag of mine costs.

00:01:29.359 --> 00:01:30.319
Thirty thousand.

00:01:32.319 --> 00:01:35.079
Once you go out, there are tons of chances to make money.

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:37.280
Asi.

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.680
Think about it.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:40.879
Call me when you've decided.

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:42.480
I'll set it up for you.

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:44.640
Go out there.

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:46.359
The sky's the limit.

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:55.400
Come on, come on, girls.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.799
Get off and go check in.

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:02.359
Brother.

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:04.280
Um, after we check in later,

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:05.599
can we come out and look around?

00:02:05.879 --> 00:02:07.799
Sure, we have free time today.

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:09.120
Tomorrow we go to the factory for orientation.

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:09.439
Okay.

00:02:09.439 --> 00:02:09.960
Let's check in first.

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:47.280
Where is this?

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:49.800
Let me out! Let me out!

00:02:50.840 --> 00:02:51.400
Quiet!

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.680
Let me out!

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:57.439
Let me out!

00:02:57.439 --> 00:02:58.520
Stop screaming! Stop screaming!

00:02:59.199 --> 00:03:00.479
You're going to get me killed.

00:03:09.439 --> 00:03:10.199
Come here.

00:03:11.319 --> 00:03:12.400
You have to know the rules.

00:03:13.919 --> 00:03:14.759
Or else.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.840
I knew I couldn't escape.

00:03:22.479 --> 00:03:23.520
To survive,

00:03:25.319 --> 00:03:27.000
I had to be at their mercy.

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:34.000
No!

00:03:37.719 --> 00:03:38.800
Shui Ge.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:42.360
Isn't that the Jerk who collected debt from me?

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:43.680
Yes.

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:45.520
He really does every kind of dirty deed.

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:51.919
What happened next?

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:55.120
Later, they trusted me.

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:58.199
And took me to the scam compound's Live-streaming base.

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:05.199
I believe in clear rewards and punishments.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.000
As long as your performance is good,

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:09.319
you can get promoted and a raise.

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:12.800
But if your performance is bad,

00:04:14.199 --> 00:04:15.520
don't blame me for getting nasty.

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:17.959
Understood?

00:04:18.639 --> 00:04:19.920
Understood.

00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:20.800
Louder!

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:21.600
Understood?

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.199
Understood! Understood!

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:36.240
You're usually the loudest one.

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:37.600
Now you're mute.

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:42.439
Understood?

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:43.720
Understood.

00:04:46.480 --> 00:04:48.120
Since you're here, you might as well settle in.

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:50.839
As long as you maximize

00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:52.279
your personal value,

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:54.319
you can create a beautiful future.

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:55.319
Left with no choice,

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:57.160
I could only do as they ordered.

00:04:57.759 --> 00:04:58.959
My grandma is sick.

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.399
She has cancer.

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.360
She needs surgery.

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:04.240
It costs a lot of money.

00:05:07.439 --> 00:05:08.759
Are you really willing to help me?

00:05:13.040 --> 00:05:14.560
Then I'll send you the card number.

00:05:19.079 --> 00:05:20.040
Thank you.

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.240
When my grandma gets better,

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:23.959
I'll go to your city to see you.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:31.480
Have one.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.120
I don't smoke.

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:35.040
Thanks.

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:38.319
Where did you get the cigarettes?

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:41.560
I asked for them.

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:43.519
Do you want to get out?

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.519
We can't escape.

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:54.360
Every day I dream of marrying a rich man and living in luxury.

00:05:57.759 --> 00:06:00.800
But look at us now.

00:06:03.879 --> 00:06:05.720
Their spies are everywhere in Tai Cheng.

00:06:06.199 --> 00:06:07.639
Even if you managed to escape,

00:06:07.639 --> 00:06:09.240
they would just catch you and bring you back.

00:06:09.519 --> 00:06:11.160
Then it would only be worse than it is now.

00:06:11.439 --> 00:06:12.160
But what if?

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:14.800
What if there's a miracle?

00:06:16.199 --> 00:06:17.839
Anyway, as long as there's a chance to run,

00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:19.759
I definitely won't hesitate.

00:06:22.360 --> 00:06:23.360
You won't tell anyone, right?

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:27.279
I don't know anything.

00:06:31.199 --> 00:06:32.720
It doesn't matter if you tell.

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:36.399
I'll just say you taught me.

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:53.399
So you want to run?

00:06:57.480 --> 00:06:59.000
Didn't I tell you?

00:06:59.199 --> 00:07:00.920
You need to work hard on your performance.

00:07:01.879 --> 00:07:02.959
Why won't you listen?

00:07:03.319 --> 00:07:05.319
Work hard on your performance and you can leave here.

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.800
Don't cross the line.

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:13.600
If you don't work hard, you'll end up like her.

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:26.560
You want to run away too?

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:27.920
Come here.

00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:30.920
I didn't.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:31.920
You come here.

00:07:32.439 --> 00:07:33.399
I can't.

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:35.839
Take it.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:37.000
Come on.

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:41.480
Prove that this has nothing to do with you.

00:07:42.959 --> 00:07:43.720
Shoot.

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:48.000
I'll count for you.

00:07:48.519 --> 00:07:48.959
Three.

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:49.639
Shoot!

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:52.360
Two.

00:08:05.480 --> 00:08:06.160
Just like that,

00:08:07.399 --> 00:08:08.759
I became a murderer.

00:08:12.199 --> 00:08:13.920
That was the nightmare of my life.

00:08:15.439 --> 00:08:17.319
Then how did you escape?

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:18.920
After that day,

00:08:20.519 --> 00:08:22.519
I had nightmares every night.

00:08:24.959 --> 00:08:27.519
I was so dazed I couldn't work properly.

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:32.279
So I suffered a lot of abuse and beatings.

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.320
But in my heart,

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:38.120
something was always calling out.

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:41.200
Rather than living in fear every day like this,

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:42.679
I might as well give it a shot.

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:45.759
Finally, one day,

00:08:46.519 --> 00:08:47.799
my chance came.

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:49.480
Quick!

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:50.759
Quick, quick! Get down!

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:52.919
Go! Hurry up!

00:08:53.039 --> 00:08:53.399
Go!

00:08:56.039 --> 00:08:56.799
Get back here!

00:09:04.039 --> 00:09:05.080
Stop! Come back!

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.000
Please.

00:09:11.799 --> 00:09:12.600
Save me.

00:09:13.799 --> 00:09:15.240
Please save me.

00:09:25.039 --> 00:09:25.679
Don't move

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:27.879
You're badly injured

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:29.480
Just rest and recover here for now

00:09:31.679 --> 00:09:32.720
Who are you?

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:36.480
Who I am isn't important

00:09:36.759 --> 00:09:38.039
Where is this?

00:09:38.519 --> 00:09:39.759
This is my private hospital

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:42.799
Don't worry, it's safe

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:46.200
Then this must be expensive

00:09:49.879 --> 00:09:52.279
Don't worry. Since I saved you,

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:53.720
I'll take care of you until the end

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:58.159
Thank you

00:09:58.519 --> 00:09:59.000
Thank you

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:00.879
Don't move. Rest well

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:01.960
From that day on,

00:10:02.639 --> 00:10:04.519
I began following Mr. Zhao

00:10:05.759 --> 00:10:07.720
and started working as a housekeeper in his home

00:10:08.799 --> 00:10:10.720
I did that for six years

00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:17.519
And the Madam, she...

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:20.679
came to Mr. Zhao's side four years ago

00:10:28.919 --> 00:10:29.600
Later,

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:32.720
Mr. Zhao bought this villa

00:10:33.559 --> 00:10:34.720
and gave it to the Madam

00:10:36.679 --> 00:10:38.320
You... what are you laughing at?

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:41.120
A housekeeper. So touching.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:46.600
Ghost!

00:10:48.519 --> 00:10:49.480
There's a ghost outside the window!

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:53.120
Who can get this crazy woman out of here?

00:10:53.679 --> 00:10:54.399
I saw it

00:10:54.799 --> 00:10:56.480
I saw a ghost

00:10:57.159 --> 00:10:57.960
I'll go out and check

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.399
Inspector Qi, I'll go with you

00:11:04.840 --> 00:11:05.600
Auntie Ma Shan

00:11:06.039 --> 00:11:07.120
Don't think too much

00:11:07.639 --> 00:11:08.559
Get some rest early

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:11.000
Asi

00:11:12.799 --> 00:11:14.000
Do you believe what I said?

00:11:15.679 --> 00:11:16.919
You are the Madam's elder

00:11:17.279 --> 00:11:18.519
so you are my elder

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:20.120
I believe you

00:11:21.519 --> 00:11:22.320
Good

00:11:22.919 --> 00:11:24.120
Call them all over

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:26.960
I want to tell my story

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:28.519
Okay

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:31.279
Inspector Qi

00:11:31.879 --> 00:11:33.799
what illness do you think Ma Shan has?

00:11:34.399 --> 00:11:37.200
Obviously, she suffered a severe shock

00:11:37.879 --> 00:11:39.440
which caused mental issues

00:11:44.600 --> 00:11:45.679
Do you really believe in ghosts?

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:48.960
I actually hope there really are ghosts

00:11:49.279 --> 00:11:50.080
That way,

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:53.159
maybe we sisters could see each other again

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:56.080
You aren't afraid?

00:11:57.320 --> 00:11:58.080
I am

00:11:58.639 --> 00:12:00.720
But people are scarier

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:04.279
Inspector Qi

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:05.159
tell me,

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:07.240
regarding my sister and brother-in-law's deaths,

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:08.440
is there anything suspicious?

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:13.600
Since we're here,

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:15.399
let's listen to the stories first

00:12:16.759 --> 00:12:17.919
Maybe the stories to follow

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:19.879
will be even more interesting

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:24.000
I...

00:12:24.679 --> 00:12:25.799
am not a lunatic

00:12:32.840 --> 00:12:33.360
Darn it

00:12:34.039 --> 00:12:34.440
This... this...

00:12:34.840 --> 00:12:36.440
We waited all this time just for this one sentence?

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:39.159
Mr. Zhao, don't be in such a hurry

00:12:40.559 --> 00:12:41.919
Everyone present here,

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:43.559
except for Inspector Qi,

00:12:44.080 --> 00:12:44.919
everyone else

00:12:45.159 --> 00:12:48.480
has some connection with Mr. Zhao and Di Fu

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:51.720
Only I am an outsider

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:54.000
Di Fu,

00:12:54.919 --> 00:12:56.120
or call her Li Ren

00:12:56.639 --> 00:12:57.639
Right, Miss Li?

00:12:59.399 --> 00:13:00.080
Yes

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:02.519
My sister's real name was Li Ren

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:04.759
Li Ren

00:13:05.639 --> 00:13:07.840
was my daughter Nana's good friend

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.720
That was in 2008